## Summary

1. **Validation-first development** - No engineering without validated demand
2. **AI-assisted discovery mandatory** - Manus, ChatGPT, Cursor, ElevenLabs, Midjourney/Canva
3. **Required discovery documents** - Niche Intelligence, Pain Signals, JTBD, Opportunity & Moat
4. **Prioritization criteria** - Urgency, willingness-to-pay, recurring jobs, data moats, workflow embedding
5. **Boring pain over novel ideas** - Favor inevitable pain over nice-to-have features
6. **Opportunity Score gate** - ≥ 8.0/10 required to proceed
7. **Quality gates enforced** - All discovery documents must pass quality checks

**This philosophy is non-negotiable. All product ideas must follow this process before engineering begins.**
